### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api
@token = seu-token-jwt-aqui

### ============================================
### CRÉDITOS
### ============================================

### Adicionar créditos
POST {{baseUrl}}/credits/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 100.00
}

### Consultar saldo
GET {{baseUrl}}/credits/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### PRODUTOS (Admin/Organizador)
### ============================================

### Criar produto
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "eventId": "event-uuid",
  "name": "Cerveja Artesanal",
  "description": "Cerveja artesanal premium",
  "price": 15.50,
  "category": "BEBIDA",
  "image": "https://example.com/cerveja.jpg",
  "isActive": true
}

### Listar produtos do evento
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/event/event-uuid?activeOnly=true

### Obter produto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/product-uuid

### Atualizar produto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/product-uuid
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Cerveja Artesanal Premium",
  "price": 18.00,
  "isActive": true
}

### Deletar produto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/product-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### PEDIDOS (Cliente)
### ============================================

### Criar pedido (comprar produtos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "eventId": "event-uuid",
  "ticketId": "ticket-uuid",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "product-uuid-1",
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": "product-uuid-2",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Obter comanda do evento
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/event/event-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter detalhes do pedido
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/order-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### VALIDAÇÃO (Atendente)
### ============================================

### Validar QR code de produto (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/validate?code=PRODUCT_abc123...&validatedBy=scanner-uuid

### Validar QR code de produto (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "PRODUCT_abc123...",
  "validatedBy": "scanner-uuid"
}

